==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Contribution plan
<hw>Con`tri*bu"tion plan</hw>. <fld>(Life Insurance)</fld> <def>A plan
of distributing surplus by giving to each policy the excess of premiums
and interest earned thereon over the expenses of management, cost of
insurance, and the policy value at the date of computation. This excess
is called the <xex>contribution</xex> of the policy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Contributive</ent>⟦br⟧
